From Peer B --->|(B)-|Path     |-->|Local-RIB|-[B]|--->To Peer B
From Peer C --->|(C)-|Selection|   |         |-[C]|--->To Peer C
From Peer D --->|(D)-|_________|   |_________|-[D]|--->To Peer D
